	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissime vir et pater in Christo summe colende, binas uno atque eodem die abs te literas accepi, alteras 11. alteras 12. septembris scriptas, ex quibus convenire ea, quae ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> accepimus, cum iis, quae etiam ad vos perlata sunt, imprimis intellexi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod igitur hac immani et perfida caede piorum tantum efferuntur papistae, signum iudico fore eo maturioris vindictae, quae illis immineat a domino.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quis enim vel immanissimarum gentium sapiens hoc nefandum scelus approbaverit?</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Consolatur igitur Christi sententia dicentis:</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">"Amen, amen dico vobis, plorabitis et lamentabimini vos; mundus contra gaudebit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vos autem moerore afficiemini; sed moeror vester vertetur in gaudium."</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quas secum unica <placeName type="auto_name">Zachariae</placeName> lapidatio poenas paulo post traxerit, notum est ex historia.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim his exemplis de agenda poenitentia et fide in invocatione seria et assidua exercenda admonemur.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proxima dominica d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p264" cert="high">doctor Burgoverus</persName> in publico diversorio offendit literas <placeName ref="l361" cert="high">Neroberga</placeName> hospiti nescio a quo traditas ad tuam pertinentes humanitatem, quas, quantum ex pictura coniicere possum, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p850" cert="high">Durnhoferi</persName> esse iudico; eas cum hoc nuncio nunc demum mitto, cum praeter hunc maturius nullus alias offerretur.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Remitto et d. doctoris <persName type="auto_name">Ursini</persName> literas, pro quarum communicatione summas tibi gratias ago.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nec materiam nec ocium plura scribendi in hoc praesertim nunc vindemiali strepitu et summa nuncii festinatione habeo.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid tua humanitas acceperit vel ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> vel ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgio</placeName>, nobis ut paucis communicet oro.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale in Christo.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant humanitatem tuam reverenter d. d. consules, doctores <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2553" cert="high">Peyerus</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p264" cert="high">Burgoverus</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Beatus Leo</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3043" cert="high">Benedictus Stockerus</persName> [Stokar, Stockar] iunior et ministri omnes et singuli.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluto reverenter omnes symmystas <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinos</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum festinantissime 18. septembris anno domini 1572.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuae humanitatis studiosissimus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8109" cert="high">Iohannes Conradus Ulmerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro atque eximio Iesu Christi servo d. <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Henrico Bullingero</persName> seniori, ecclesiae <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinae</placeName> antistiti fidelissimo, domino et patri suo in Christo summe colendo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An den ehrwirdigen, hochgelehrten herren <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Heinrichen Bullinger</persName>n den eltern, dienern der kirchen <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
